data.description: Welcome to your new happy place in the heart of Shively! This charming 4-bedroom, 1-bathroom home is bursting with character and ready to become your ultimate sanctuary. This 1300 square foot gem is bursting with personality, offering ample space for your imagination to run wild. Picture lazy Sundays in the sunny backyard, sizzling up BBQ feasts, and hosting game nights with friends. Plus, with top-notch schools, parks, and local hotspots just a hop, skip, and a jump away, every day in this delightful abode is bound to be a blast! Don't miss out on this slice of suburban paradise - schedule your showing today and let the good times roll!
